,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T18:01:40.000Z","msg":"點"},{"pid":"9fd1cf9b8e6b99e6398a32bbbd4fcb8f2bddb16f","tid":328660,"uid":6031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T18:03:49.000Z","msg":"俾公司炒咗，聽日又廢青生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848d6307b6fe7e7f8b338dceee1b1f913314dfa4","tid":328660,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T18:04:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾公司炒咗，聽日又廢青生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做錯野？畀人屌得好甘？"},{"pid":"a672925e3a66c590babb7d33c301a738d65d4409","tid":328660,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T18:04:55.000Z","msg":"佢地覺得你勁姐"},{"pid":"250c5fc1a4e40c14a0de85c261d01685d9387004","tid":328660,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T18:06:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾公司炒咗，聽日又廢青生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n願聞其詳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nYou are not alone"},{"pid":"ef3845f68370814c7c63137e46ec0e1861e2424f","tid":328660,"uid":6031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T18:09:48.000Z","msg":"我諗純粹因爲上司私怨唔鍾意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但第一次俾人炒真係不太好受<br />\n<br />\n夜晚想同啲朋友飲嘢<br />\n個朋友係我同另一半嘅共同朋友，咁仲有多幾個共同朋友嘅<br />\n無啦啦有個人話唔嚟（我未見過佢）<br />\n因為佢識我另一半嘅ex，話唔想複雜化啲關係所以唔嚟，搞咗成粒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似我坐喺到已經影響到成班人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53aed1019d090084cc69cf7cf52885ed31c86d1c","tid":328660,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T18:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5856f58f9a8b92ed157a1be9f7edaae9c1d7